The program calculates what contributions need to be made monthly so that the amount will be enough for the planned period
The data is taken from the intut.txt file. It contains explanations for the data. The amounts are stored in kopecks inside the program.

It is assumed that contributions will be made monthly from the calculation date to your own pension
fund on the IIS until the retirement date. Then the funds will be spent in the desired amount, adjusted for inflation.
The portfolio will consist of shares/bonds at the beginning 70/30, in the last 7 years the balance has changed in favor of conservative instruments.